{
  "stem": "19895.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were talking about the children, which they didn't know where they were, because they were coming from the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother could make this food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother could make that food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody cooked like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so on.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those were the conversations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Needs of cigarettes among those who were very much hooked on being a-- habitual cigarette smokers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't have cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Occasionally, some of the guards were throwing the butts of the cigarettes to them and they picked it up from the floor still-- still smoking.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they were like seven heaven if they could smoke that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And dried leaves, dried leaves, dried out and broken up, rolled into some paper foil or dried papers were the way to-- to supplement cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did they have matches?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how, but somehow some people had even a simple cigarette lighter, which still had some-- some things in it to light up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, myself, started to roll dry leafs because I wanted to be part of the scene.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when-- when-- when I came back to Budapest after I was freed from the concentration camp, what was next for me?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I became a cigarette smoker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I smoked till I was around 40 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I gave up now 28 years ago, on the urging of my children, says you are a doctor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You should know how bad it does.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And finally, I listened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I gave up 28 years ago, smoking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But smoking was, again, something which people missed tremendously and-- and-- and-- they were substituting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as a child, I remember that-- that-- what a pleasure it was to them even to inhale and then-- then smoke that awful smelling dry leaf.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Disease, typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People were dying left and right.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
